title: Is This Aracely Henriquez, the Woman George Floyd Allegedly Assaulted?
subtitle: The police encounter that led to Floyd's death in Minneapolis in 2020 was centered around reports about a counterfeit $20 bill, not any of his past actions.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A photograph shows Aracely Henriquez, a woman who was allegedly assaulted by George Floyd in a robbery.
